            . I am one of the beadles of St. Bride's, I produce the register of 
               <persName id="t18110109-8-person147">
                  Charles 
                  Handyside
               <interp inst="t18110109-8-person147" type="surname" value="Handyside"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18110109-8-person147" type="given" value="Charles"></interp>
